titleStmt.title: Whereas for divers yeeres there hath not been any election of schollers in the College of Eaton, and this yeer by reason there was no provost setled in Kings Colledge in Cambridge, the it is there fore ordained by the Lords and Commons assembled in Parliament, that there may, and shall be an election of schollers in manner as hath been heretofore accustomed before the thirtieth day of October next following ...

Whereas for divers yeeres there hath not been any election of schollers in the College of Eaton, and this yeer by reason there was no provost setled in Kings Colledge in Cambridge, the it is there fore ordained by the Lords and Commons assembled in Parliament, that there may, and shall be an election of schollers in manner as hath been heretofore accustomed before the thirtieth day of October next following ...

notesStmt.note: At head of title : die Jovis 28. August. 1645.
